            </div>
            <p class="govuk-body">When we provide services, we want to make them easy, useful and reliable. Our website puts small
                files (known as 'cookies') onto your computer to collect information about how you browse the site.</p>
            <p class="govuk-body">Cookies are used to:</p>
            <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
                <li>measure how you use the website so it can be updated and improved based on your needs</li>
                <li>remember the notifications you've seen so that we don't show them to you again</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="govuk-inset-text">
                Cookies on food.gov.uk are not used to identify you personally.
            </div>
            <h2 class="govuk-heading-l" id="change-your-cookie-settings">Change your cookie settings</h2>
            <p class="govuk-body">You can change which cookies you're happy for us to use:</p>
            <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
                <li>
                    <a class="govuk-link" href="https://www.food.gov.uk/cookie-consent?dest=/cookie-policy">Change cookie settings on
                        food.gov.uk</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a
                        class="govuk-link"
                        href="https://ratings.food.gov.uk/cookie-consent?dest=/cookie-policy"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener">Change cookie settings on ratings.food.gov.uk (opens in a new tab)</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="govuk-body">
                <a class="govuk-link" href="https://ico.org.uk/for-the-public/online/cookies/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Find out
                    more about how to manage cookies (opens in a new tab)</a>
            </p>
            <h2 class="govuk-heading-l" id="cookies-on-food-gov-uk">Cookies on food.gov.uk and ratings.food.gov.uk</h2>
            <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Strictly necessary cookies</h3>
            <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Session ID</h4>
            <p class="govuk-body">
                <strong>Name:</strong>
                JSESSIONID and PHPSESSID<br>
                    <strong>Purpose:</strong>
                    Used to maintain an anonymous user session by the server<br>
                        <strong>Expires:</strong>
                        After the end of the user session
                    </p>
                    <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Cookies message</h4>
                    <p class="govuk-body">
                        <strong>Name:</strong>
                        cookie-preferences, cookieconsent_dismissed<br>
                            <strong>Purpose:</strong>
                            Used to remember whether you accepted or declined optional cookies
                        </p>
                        <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Cloudflare</h4>
                        <p class="govuk-body">
                            <strong>Name:</strong>
                            __cfduid<br>
                                <strong>Purpose:</strong>
                                Set to identify trusted web traffic. Does not store any personally identifiable information<br>
                                    <strong>Expires:</strong>
                                    5 years
                                </p>
                                <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Cookies that measure website use</h3>
                                <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Google Analytics</h4>
                                <p class="govuk-body">We use Google Analytics software to collect information about how you use food.gov.uk. We do this
                                    to help make sure the site is meeting the needs of its users and to help us make improvements. We don't allow Google to
                                    use or share our analytics data.</p>
                                <table class="govuk-table">
                                    <thead class="govuk-table__head">
                                        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
                                            <th class="govuk-table__header" scope="col">Name</th>
                                            <th class="govuk-table__header" scope="col">Purpose</th>
                                            <th class="govuk-table__header" scope="col">Expires</th>
                                        </tr>
                                    </thead>
                                    <tbody class="govuk-table__body">
                                        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">_ga</td>
                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">Counts visitors by tracking if you have visited before</td>
                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">2 years</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">_gid</td>
                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">Counts visitors by tracking if you have visited before</td>
                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">24 hours</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">_gat</td>
                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">Manages the rate at which page view requests are made. Does not store user information</td>
                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">Set by Google</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">_utma</td>
                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">Lets us know if you have visited before, so we can count new visitors</td>
                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">2 years</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">_utmb</td>
                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">Works with _utmc to calculate average time spent on food.gov.uk</td>
                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">30 minutes</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">_utmc</td>
                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">Works with _utmb to calculate when you close your browser</td>
                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">When you close your browser</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">_utmz</td>
                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">Tells us how you reached food.gov.uk (for example from another website or a search engine)</td>
                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">6 months</td>
                                        </tr>
                                    </tbody>
                                </table>
                                <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">SiteImprove</h4>
                                <p class="govuk-body">
                                    <strong>Name:</strong>
                                    nmstat<br>
                                        <strong>Purpose:</strong>
                                        Statistics about site usage such as when you last visited the site<br>
                                            <strong>Expires:</strong>
                                            1000 days after last visit
                                        </p>
                                        <p class="govuk-body">
                                            <strong>Name:</strong>
                                            AWSELB / AWSELBCOR<br>
                                                <strong>Purpose:</strong>
                                                Set by SiteImprove to determine the sequence of page views to understand user journeys<br>
                                                    <strong>Expires:</strong>
                                                    When you exit your browser
                                                </p>
                                                <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Cookies that help with communications and marketing</h3>
                                                <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">YouTube cookies</h4>
                                                <p class="govuk-body">We use YouTube to provide videos on some pages of the site. YouTube sets cookies when you visit
                                                    one of these pages.</p>
                                                <table class="govuk-table">
                                                    <thead class="govuk-table__head">
                                                        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
                                                            <th class="govuk-table__header" scope="col">Name</th>
                                                            <th class="govuk-table__header" scope="col">Purpose</th>
                                                            <th class="govuk-table__header" scope="col">Expires</th>
                                                        </tr>
                                                    </thead>
                                                    <tbody class="govuk-table__body">
                                                        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
                                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">use_hitbox</td>
                                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">Randomly generated number that identifies your browser</td>
                                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">When you close your browser</td>
                                                        </tr>
                                                        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
                                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">VISITOR_INFO1_LIVE</td>
                                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">Lets YouTube count the views of embedded videos</td>
                                                            <td class="govuk-table__cell">9 months</td>
                                                        </tr>
                                                    </tbody>
                                                </table>
                                                <h2 class="govuk-heading-l" id="cookies-on-other-fsa-websites">Cookies on other FSA websites</h2>
                                                <p class="govuk-body">Cookies on other FSA websites cannot be managed from the cookie consent page on food.gov.uk. You
                                                    can manage cookies on these websites using your browser controls.</p>
                                                <p class="govuk-body">
                                                    <a class="govuk-link" href="https://ico.org.uk/for-the-public/online/cookies/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Find out
                                                        more about how to manage cookies (opens in a new tab)</a>
                                                </p>
                                                <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Food allergy and intolerance training (allergytraining.food.gov.uk)</h3>
                                                <p class="govuk-body">
                                                    <strong>Name:</strong>
                                                    MoodleSession<br>
                                                        <strong>Purpose:</strong>
                                                        Provides continuity and maintains user login from page to page<br>
                                                            <strong>Expires:</strong>
                                                            When you log out or close your browser
                                                        </p>
                                                        <p class="govuk-body">
                                                            <strong>Name:</strong>
                                                            MoodleID<br>
                                                                <strong>Purpose:</strong>
                                                                Records the username when you log in and allows the username field to be automatically filled in the next time you
                                                                visit
                                                            </p>
                                                            <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">MyHACCP web tool (food.gov.uk/myhaccp)</h3>
                                                            <p class="govuk-body">
                                                                <strong>Name:</strong>
                                                                SESS[Unique ID]<br>
                                                                    <strong>Purpose:</strong>
                                                                    Allows logging in and interacting with the MyHACCP service; essential for MyHACCP site functionality<br>
                                                                        <strong>Expires:</strong>
                                                                        23 days
                                                                    </p>
                                                                    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Register a food business service</h3>
                                                                    <p class="govuk-body">
                                                                        <strong>Name:</strong>
                                                                        connect.sid<br>
                                                                            <strong>Purpose:</strong>
                                                                            Used to persist registration data<br>
                                                                                <strong>Expires:</strong>
                                                                                24 hours
                                                                            </p>
                                                                            <p class="govuk-body">
                                                                                <strong>Name:</strong>
                                                                                _gid<br>
                                                                                    <strong>Purpose:</strong>
                                                                                    Helps us count how many people visit the service by tracking if you have visited before<br>
                                                                                        <strong>Expires:</strong>
                                                                                        3 days
                                                                                    </p>
                                                                                    <h2 class="govuk-heading-l" id="cookies-on-sac-sites">Cookies on Scientific Advisory Committees sites</h2>
                                                                                    <p class="govuk-body">Scientific Advisory Committees (SAC) sites have their own cookie policy. Find out more about
                                                                                        <a class="govuk-link" href="https://ico.org.uk/for-the-public/online/cookies/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">cookies on
                                                                                            SAC sites (opens in a new tab)</a>.</p>
                                                                                    <p class="govuk-body">Other websites and services we link to may set additional cookies and will have their own cookie
                                                                                        policy. This includes other government services and social media platforms.</p>
                                                                                    {# ── Revision log ───────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
